Gunther Ave., adjoining and at the S.E. corner of Astor Ave. The large house, adjoining the corner, bears No. 2238, and the corner house bears No. 1726 on Astor Ave. They are in the residential section known as Pelham Parkway Gardens.
About 1923.
Joseph P. Day.
